{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"54b6106c4d","title":"周恩来就国民党伪造“伍豪等脱离共党启事”一事给毛泽东的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"45b09232ba","index":0,"year":1967,"month":5,"day":19,"articleId":"54b6106c4d"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"4206ce6bf3","name":"红卫兵运动","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"523bb79e8f","name":"周恩来","type":"人物"},{"id":"56a499f88d","name":"上海文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"57eea82497","name":"康生","type":"人物"},{"id":"82305e518c","name":"江青","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"7a99cebe4e","name":"周恩来"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"f667e35c15","type":"title","text":"周恩来就国民党伪造“伍豪等脱离共党启事”一事给毛泽东的信","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"54b6106c4d"},{"id":"90aea41dcf","type":"authors","text":"周恩来","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"54b6106c4d"},{"id":"6367249ef3","type":"appellation","text":"主席：","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"54b6106c4d"},{"id":"e821989b5d","type":"paragraph","text":"连日因忙于四川和内蒙问题，并同内蒙军区请愿战士分批谈话，直到今天才抽出一天功夫翻阅上海各报，江青同志也于昨日转来各件，现在弄清楚了所谓“伍豪等启事”，就是1932年2月28日的伪造启事，它是先在《新闻报》2月28日登出的。登后，同天，上海临时中央方面就向申报馆设法，结果，《申报》20日、21日登出伪造的启事，22日登了广告处给伍豪先生另一广告启事的拒登回答，大概这是当时所能做到的公开否认伪造启事的办法。我在记忆中，有通过申报馆设法否认的处置，但结果不明，16日午间已向主席这样说了。不过我原来将伪造的伍豪启事记在通缉杀人犯周恩来、赵容（即康生）之前，现在证明是我记错了，查遍1931年顾顺章、向忠发相继叛变后的上海各报，并无另一个所谓伍豪启事，而红卫兵也未发现另一启事。可见在我记忆中的伪造启事和通过申报馆设法的处置，均在我到江西后发生的，所以我只能从电报和来信中知道，也就不全了然了。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"54b6106c4d"},{"id":"316179a5c3","type":"paragraph","text":"现在，把四中全会后与此有关的编为大事记送阅，同时，送上报道最详的上海《时报》1931年11月12月合订本一册，《申报》1932年1月2月合订本两册，请翻阅。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"54b6106c4d"},{"id":"6948e535a2","type":"paragraph","text":"此事需否专写一报告，待主席、林彪、康生、江青各同志传阅送上各件后，请再约谈一次，好作定夺。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"54b6106c4d"},{"id":"317fbc2475","type":"appellation","text":"敬礼！","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"54b6106c4d"},{"id":"76db70e62d","type":"paragraph","text":" 周恩来五月十九日夜","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"54b6106c4d"},{"id":"3d85e45e82","type":"paragraph","text":"附件","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"54b6106c4d"},{"id":"c6def02331","type":"subtitle","text":"大事记","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"54b6106c4d"},{"id":"2be8d3a1f9","type":"subtitle","text":"1931年","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"54b6106c4d"},{"id":"83edded0ff","type":"paragraph","text":"1月，中央开六届四中全会","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"54b6106c4d"},{"id":"49f9770908","type":"paragraph","text":"4月，顾顺章送张国焘、陈昌浩等经武汉入鄂豫皖苏区，顾留汉口被捕，向蒋介石自首。","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"54b6106c4d"},{"id":"5ceef10f9f","type":"paragraph","text":"上海当夜得到消息，中央有关机关全部转移。5月，中央决定消灭顾顺章家属10人。","index":13,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"54b6106c4d"},{"id":"bcacf1a18b","type":"paragraph","text":"6月，向忠发捕后叛变，处死。有两处机关破坏。","index":14,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"54b6106c4d"},{"id":"2c3f9cf7f6","type":"paragraph","text":"9月，九·一八沈阳被日寇侵占。","index":15,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"54b6106c4d"},{"id":"063fc6b5af","type":"paragraph","text":"11月，特科王世德（老先生）被捕，供出顾顺章家属被消灭。","index":16,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"54b6106c4d"},{"id":"3cc4880c17","type":"paragraph","text":"11月21日，国民党下令发掘尸身，在法租界姚主教路爱棠村37号，33号，胶济路，武定路、德坊6号，在新闸路，麦特赫斯脱路陈家巷91号，从21日至28日先后掘出男女尸身各8具，共16人。","index":17,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"54b6106c4d"},{"id":"61a773f541","type":"paragraph","text":"报上登出的有：","index":18,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"54b6106c4d"},{"id":"d33488acb0","type":"paragraph","text":"时报（22日至25日，27日至29日7天）；","index":19,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"54b6106c4d"},{"id":"e58c40e75d","type":"paragraph","text":"申报（23日至28日6天）；","index":20,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"54b6106c4d"},{"id":"2f4ade9d0f","type":"paragraph","text":"新闻报（22日，24日至29日7天）；","index":21,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"54b6106c4d"},{"id":"01b03bc0a8","type":"paragraph","text":"时事新报（24日至30日7天）；","index":22,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"54b6106c4d"},{"id":"5462240075","type":"paragraph","text":"民国日报（24日至27日4天）。","index":23,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"54b6106c4d"},{"id":"a94858f5d9","type":"paragraph","text":"登得最详并附照片的为时报。（附一专讯）","index":24,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"54b6106c4d"},{"id":"76e8c21131","type":"paragraph","text":"11月底至12月初","index":25,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"54b6106c4d"},{"id":"c50a306eb7","type":"paragraph","text":"顾顺章悬赏缉拿杀人凶手周恩来等紧要启事（全文附）","index":26,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"54b6106c4d"},{"id":"87e3a5682f","type":"paragraph","text":"报上登出的有：","index":27,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"54b6106c4d"},{"id":"6acc52c710","type":"paragraph","text":"时报（11月29日至30日，12月1至2日4天）；","index":28,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"54b6106c4d"},{"id":"3b9928d197","type":"paragraph","text":"申报（11月29日至30日，12月1日3天）；","index":29,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"54b6106c4d"},{"id":"16f9252a7e","type":"paragraph","text":"新闻报（11月29日至30日11月1至2日4天）；","index":30,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"54b6106c4d"},{"id":"40662351a1","type":"paragraph","text":"时事新报（11月29日至30日，12月1至3日5天）；","index":31,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"54b6106c4d"},{"id":"be0e118dec","type":"paragraph","text":"民国日报（11 月29至30日，12月1至2日4天）。","index":32,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"54b6106c4d"},{"id":"cf1a564c64","type":"paragraph","text":"12月上旬周离沪，经汕头，从永定进入中央苏区。在闽西得知12月14日宁都暴动五军团起义成功。","index":33,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"54b6106c4d"},{"id":"579f9a975c","type":"paragraph","text":"20日左右，周抵瑞金叶坪。","index":34,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"54b6106c4d"},{"id":"ec2efc8309","type":"subtitle","text":"1932年","index":35,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"54b6106c4d"},{"id":"897b5b3d43","type":"paragraph","text":"1月，王世德发表叛变声明（全文附）","index":36,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"54b6106c4d"},{"id":"bc1d044099","type":"paragraph","text":"上海登1月11日申报，其他报未见。","index":37,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"54b6106c4d"},{"id":"a53cd854ac","type":"paragraph","text":"据报，南京中央日报登1月2日。","index":38,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"54b6106c4d"},{"id":"0c6a48d730","type":"paragraph","text":"1月28日，淞沪抗战。","index":39,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"54b6106c4d"},{"id":"a5a20a982b","type":"paragraph","text":"2月，18日起至21日，上海报上先后登出敌人伪造的“伍豪等脱离共党启事”（全文附）。号称243人，并无另一姓名，就此一点，断然为敌伪造无疑。","index":40,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"54b6106c4d"},{"id":"9fab9b1d35","type":"paragraph","text":"上海报上登的有：","index":41,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"54b6106c4d"},{"id":"77cd909767","type":"paragraph","text":"新闻报（2月18日，19日）；","index":42,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"54b6106c4d"},{"id":"2395057bfb","type":"paragraph","text":"申报（2月20日，21日）；","index":43,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"54b6106c4d"},{"id":"fdadd9544e","type":"paragraph","text":"时事新报（2月20日，21日）；","index":44,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"54b6106c4d"},{"id":"53b75e7487","type":"paragraph","text":"时报未登。","index":45,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"54b6106c4d"},{"id":"9769873240","type":"paragraph","text":"民国日报未找到。","index":46,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"54b6106c4d"},{"id":"a76d0823b1","type":"paragraph","text":"2月22日，申报在广告栏内登出如下启事：","index":47,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"54b6106c4d"},{"id":"d05511bce8","type":"paragraph","text":"“伍豪先生鉴承于本月18日送来广告启事一则，因福昌床公司否认担保，手续不合，致未刊出。申报馆广告处启。”","index":48,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"54b6106c4d"},{"id":"2d0ec14ba8","type":"paragraph","text":"这种广告处启事，登在广告栏内很少先例，而又在伪造脱党启事登报的同天，当时一望而知是否认脱党启事的，故未能登出。这想是当时党中央所采取的公开否认办法。","index":49,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"54b6106c4d"}],"page":{"id":"d8fba48f36","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"54b6106c4d","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}